These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, june, april, caring
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, chestnut, grey, brown
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, tulip, azalea, lily
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, car, snowmobile, boat
1. the person who likes chestnut is the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who growslily is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the person who growsazalea is the person who likes orange##1
4. the person who's birthday is in caring is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
5. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
7. the person who likes chestnut is the person driving the quad-bike##1
8. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
9. the person who's birthday is in caring is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday         | july  | caring  | june | april |
| Color           | chestnut | orange | brown  | grey  |
| Flower   | lily       | azalea      | amaryllis | tulip      |
| Transport           | quad-bike          | car     | snowmobile    | boat     |

