.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different games are played: go, billiard, bridge, canasta
4 different pets are kept: hamster, turtle, horse, lizard
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, january, october, june
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, musical, romance, epic
1. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person playing go##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person playing bridge is the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
8. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person playing go##1
9. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Game      | bridge     | go       | billiard | canasta        |
| Pet          | lizard     | turtle       | horse   | hamster   |
| Birthday   | october      | january       | june     | april    |
| Movie-Genre         | romance | epic | time-travel | musical |

