.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, car, bike, quad-bike
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, skateboarding, rugby, ice-hockey
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, d&b, pop, blues
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, video-games, puzzles, sudoku
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 2. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
 3. the fan of pop is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 6. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 7. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
10. the person driving the bike is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Transport      | car | helicopter       | quad-bike        | bike        |
| Sport           | skateboarding   | rugby | skiing   | ice-hockey |
| Music-Genre   | salsa     | d&b    | blues | pop        |
| Hobby           | puzzles         | baking  | sudoku       | video-games         |

