.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, aquamarine, chestnut, ivory
City: hannover, paris, prague, liverpool
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, amaryllis, balloon-flower, orchid
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, hot-chocolate, 7up
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who likes black##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
7. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes black##1
8. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Color           | aquamarine   | black  | ivory | chestnut |
| City   | prague | liverpool       | paris       | hannover     |
| Flower   | balloon-flower       | orchid    | amaryllis     | rose  |
| Beverage           | juice     | hot-chocolate | 7up     | lemonade         |

