.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, video-games, cooking, collecting
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, blood-red, emerald, mauve
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, trance, salsa, folk
4 different games are played: canasta, snooker, poker, backgammon
1. the person who likes emerald is on the far left##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
4. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the fan of folk is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person playing backgammon is the fan of salsa##1
7. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
9. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby           | board-games  | cooking    | video-games | collecting |
| Color   | emerald      | blood-red    | ebony         | mauve    |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | dubstep     | salsa          | folk      |
| Game         | snooker | canasta | backgammon      | poker      |

