 7. the fan of dubstep is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre    | superhero | time-travel     | documentary    | drama |
