4. the person eating pomegranate is the vegafina-smoker##1
5. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the nurse##1
6. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the art-deco house##1
7. the musician is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
8. the bongani-smoker is the person eating cabbage##1
9. the lawyer is on the right of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| Food      | broccoli     | cabbage           | peach    | pomegranate    |
| Cigar         | fonseca  | bongani | prince  | vegafina |
| Job   | security-guard     | lawyer     | nurse | musician   |
| House         | townhouse | wooden     | art-deco | palace     |

